r:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">是不是看到很多家长和朋友转发？</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">是不是觉得自己读过的书都还给了老师，面对这些讨厌的谣言却缺乏准确的判断？</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;text-align:center;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<img class=\"\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/JqP8jejB32SyhEaZicaicqdIS6qicFBQLoyLvY5QT2eaqaQvI2b7omI9QJ9UNFp6ibYGftKbNoL9ZgB4z6GcwS5iaQA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" style=\"height:auto !important;width:auto !important;\" />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;text-align:center;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">从你看到这篇文章开始，你将会获得一件反击谣言专用的神器——《微信辟谣助手》小程序。</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">无数的谣言像病毒一样通过朋友圈肆虐传播，微信终于也看不下去了，除了封禁了一批“有毒”的公共账号，铲除了一部分谣言的发源地，还专门推出了这款小程序，希望能加强大众对于谣言的分辨能力和抵制意识。</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">先看看这款小程序颜值如何：</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<img class=\"\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/JqP8jejB32SyhEaZicaicqdIS6qicFBQLoyORVnscgORW38y2mhmQzsAVyRY8aNfIJ4bOwxsW3LJQyIicJZXVBIuXQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" style=\"height:auto !important;width:auto !important;\" />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<img class=\"\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/JqP8jejB32SyhEaZicaicqdIS6qicFBQLoySHJibyibZLQ2UzWswZib357UaMX8wYabuq7icSUq1W0ntLEXtg0muVzLhA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" style=\"height:auto !important;width:auto !important;\" />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<img class=\"\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/JqP8jejB32SyhEaZicaicqdIS6qicFBQLoy9gYsXYQp6XZ8Uu4qIZeMIo4oFrMGrh3Otb0UTjxwGKTteQwR6Q8UAA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" style=\"height:auto !important;width:auto !important;\" />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<img class=\"\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/JqP8jejB32SyhEaZicaicqdIS6qicFBQLoyRtypkvTS9Pn2yNJ0LDAa4qgvicAKg7vMHaWsyPp7avunor4ibvJrmCQg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" style=\"height:auto !important;width:auto !important;\" />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">感觉颜值还说的过去，是微信团队的一贯风格——朴素的外表，华丽的内在。</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;\">在这里</span>，<span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;\">用户不仅可以主动搜索分辨谣言，而且可以收到阅读或者分享过的文章被鉴定为谣言的提醒。这些入驻的鉴定者，都是各个行业中的翘楚，他们只用科学和数据说话，是反击谣言最有力的武器。</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">谣言一直很难被根治，主要因为谣言帖</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;\">虽然谎话连篇，却贴近生活，且通俗易懂，极易受到网友的追捧，往往比辟谣帖更抓眼球。谣言帖的这些特点，对谣言治理形成很大的困扰，因为辟谣既要讲时效性，又要有趣味性，还要与谣言帖有大致相同的阅读群体，其难度可想而知。</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><br />\r\n而此次上线的微信辟谣助手很好地化解了治理方面的一些困扰：它除了有搜索查询功能外，还能让辟谣紧随谣言传播，谣言走到哪，辟谣就能跟到哪。这样一来，虽然真相没有跑在谣言前面，但至少可以同步呈现。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n现在，关注《轻应用商店》微信公众号，回复辟谣，即可收获这件神器哦。以后经常看一看，咱们也是辟谣专家。</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n</p>',1497518261,85,1,'');
